data.description: Experience the charm of this Craftsman-style Cape Cod home in the desirable Rosemont East neighborhood. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this residence offers both style and functionality. Upon entering, you'll be captivated by the living room's stained glass accents, lending a unique character to the space. The adjacent dining room, featuring a bay window, provides a warm and inviting atmosphere for meals and gatherings. The kitchen is a chef's dream with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample table space for casual dining. Convenience is key with one bedroom and a bath on the entry level, ideal for guests or as a home office. Venture to the upper level, where you'll find two additional bedrooms, providing privacy and comfort for all members of the household. The finished basement offers a versatile recreation/family room area, complete with a full bath and an additional bedroom. This space can easily be customized to suit your lifestyle, whether for entertaining or relaxation. Enjoy the outdoors on the covered front and rear porches or on the deck, perfect for hosting outdoor gatherings. Parking is a breeze with a driveway and a one-car detached garage, providing plenty of space for your vehicles and storage needs. Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful property in Rosemont East your new home. Explore the possibilities and schedule your viewing today!
